# Standing guard — dashboard and executive

When working on **web/app/dashboard/page.tsx** or any shared dashboard file:

- Do **not** modify, move, rename, or change import paths for any files in:
  - **web/components/dashboard/executive/**
  - **web/app/dashboard/executive/**
  - **web/app/components/dashboard/executive/**
- Do **not** change any imports that were working before this rule ran.

Apply this constraint to every prompt that touches the rep dashboard or shared dashboard code.
